caption.p: Comparison of mean sugar content by mosquito species and sex, grouped by trapping method. This data only includes Summer 2018 mosquitoes. AeF = Ae. aegypti female; AeM = Ae. aegypti male; CxF = Cx. quinquefasciatus female; CxM = Cx. quinquefasciatus male. ** indicates statistical significance between means ( P = 0.0094).
